title: "compile: reading input: EOF" errors on windows-amd64 builder
body:
Starting from ea306ae windows-amd64 builder failes with random messages like:
```
# cmd/internal/obj/x86_test
compile: reading input: EOF
ok  	cmd/internal/obj	0.040s
FAIL	cmd/internal/obj/x86 [build failed]
```
http://build.golang.org/log/859abd9846408995635e59a593e1e48ac794bb39
http://build.golang.org/log/024d163ef18c6748b539ef4acc72dee8f53ee6fa
http://build.golang.org/log/21b57103160b11601f7f5131d3a4142198d9d75f

Alex
